            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/490.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, cut the potatoes (with skins on) into bite-size chunks</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the potatoes to a pot (with a matching lid) of salted boiling water</p>\r\n<p><strong>Boil</strong> on a high heat, covered, for 10-15 min or until you can pierce them easily with a fork</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/490.-step-3-x200.jpg",
