      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the carrot ribbons (drained) and coriander to the dressing bowl and mix well</p>\r\n<p><strong>Serve</strong> the meatballs over the mash with the carrot salad to the side</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
